Package: cie11cl
Title: ICD-11 (CIE-11) Access and ICD-10 to ICD-11 Crosswalks for Chile
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Rodolfo", "Tasso", , "rtasso@uchile.cl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Deterministic access to the World Health Organization
    International Classification of Diseases, 11th Revision (ICD-11, MMS
    linearization) in Spanish, with code lookup, lexical search, hierarchical
    navigation, cluster validation, and ICD-10 to ICD-11 crosswalks with
    traceable certainty levels. The package bundles the WHO MMS 2026
    linearization (37,212 entities). The same input plus the same versioned
    reference data always yields the same output.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
